lead_paragraph: Defending champion Tomas Berdych advanced to the quarterfinals of the Shenzhen Open by beating Mikhail Kukushkin of Kazakhstan 7-6 (7), 7-6 (4) Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Tomas Berdych Through to Quarterfinals at Shenzhen Open
